## components/StaffRegistration.tsx

1.  **Field Mapping in Sync Modal**:
    *   Added a configuration section that appears after selecting a form.
    *   Provides dropdowns to map Form Fields -> System Columns (Name, Phone, Address, Age, DOB, Schedule).
    *   Includes an "Auto-Match" algorithm to pre-fill these dropdowns based on field types and labels.
    *   Unmapped fields are automatically appended to the "Notes" section.

